findMenuCounts() - Method in interface com.lambdaschool.crudyrestaurants.repositories.RestaurantRepository
Custom Query to list the name of the restaurant and the number of menu items in descending order by number of menu items SELECT r.name, count(menuid) as countmenus FROM restaurants r LEFT JOIN menus m ON r.restaurantid = m.restaurantid GROUP BY r.name ORDER BY countmenus desc
